Package: rkpairip
Version: 5.2
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, python, openjdk-17, apksigner
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/TechnoIndian/RKPairip
Description: Remove Pairip Protection and Rebuild APKs
 RKPairip is a script to remove Pairip protection from APK files,
 recover strings, and rebuild APKs. Designed for Android security
 research and reverse engineering.
